  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think `state` is not supposed to mutated, it could cause some unexpected behaviour. I think it might be better to [`.getState()`](https://community.algolia.com/algoliasearch-helper-js/reference.html#AlgoliaSearchHelper#getState), [`.setState()`](https://community.algolia.com/algoliasearch-helper-js/reference.html#AlgoliaSearchHelper#setState) and `.search` when necessary on the helper",
    "created_at": "2017-10-11T22:51:38Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2424#issuecomment-335971273",
    "id": 335971273,
    "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2424",
    "node_id": "MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDMzNTk3MTI3Mw==",
